FADE IN:

INT. WAREHOUSE - NIGHT

Empty crates stacked to the ceiling. A single flashlight beam sweeps the dark.

CUT TO:

EXT. WAREHOUSE - CONTINUOUS

A van idles outside, engine running.

SMASH CUT TO:

INT. VAN - NIGHT

DRIVER
(into radio)
We're clear. Moving now.

DISSOLVE TO:

EXT. HIGHWAY - LATER

The van merges into sparse traffic, taillights fading into the dark.

FADE TO BLACK.

> THE END <
